{"tid":1741981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅隧封咗，而家主力要玩東隧？","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T15:30:49.000Z","uid":287214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f11de678314162f75ad27c1cb5f28524422e727a","tid":1741981,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:44:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封多一條隧道，你話佢地會唔會開始焦急？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我發夢夢到以上。大家千祈唔好做犯法野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f924e61e271d32423259acc497eb1da91d69ef8","tid":1741981,"uid":51058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好封西隧呀,全部人去中環要兜大圈"},{"pid":"86765cc1c59894e5e36de498776bcc36c7f48855","tid":1741981,"uid":160383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實封隧道<br />\n只會令多左人搭黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n反而封左黨鐵，好多人就會被迫搭車同渣車<br />\n然後就會塞埋<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔建議你地咁做，而且好反對"},{"pid":"920ed628d1b1f67c6d51b7adb9d096ecc1db47dc","tid":1741981,"uid":303677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86765cc1c59894e5e36de498776bcc36c7f48855","tid":1741981,"uid":160383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實封隧道<br />\n只會令多左人搭黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n反而封左黨鐵，好多人就會被迫搭車同渣車<br />\n然後就會塞埋<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔建議你地咁做，而且好反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔好"},{"pid":"4dacbc21632084cef3d296bd458c640f4e36590f","tid":1741981,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<br />\n 雖然人係可以坐地鐵 但係貨唔可以呀 港島又無咩大型貨櫃碼頭 <br />\n如果封哂3條隧道啲貨點過去<br />\n千其唔好咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897829f344610b4a063b78f6ac9653135b905fd4","tid":1741981,"uid":27780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班警察可唔可以唔好塞住條